<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hạfḍl ạḥbk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- mhmạ hạʿdy fy wqt ṣʿb .. mhmạ qạmt ʿly ḥrb

[V2]
 mhmạ kạnt ḥyạty krb .. hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk

[V3]
 mhmạ fy wqt gẖlbny jwʿ .. ạ̉w ḥty̱ hạʿdy bwqwʿ

[V4]
 yfḍl ḥbk ly yswʿ .. hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk .. hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk

[V5]
 ạlqrạr- bạḥbk yạ yswʿ lạ̉nk ạ̹nt mʿny̱ ạlḥb

[V6]
 tfḍl ạ̹nt ạ̹lhy ạlṣạlḥ .. tfḍl ạ̹nt ạ̉myn wạ̉b

[V7]
 2- mhmạ ḥsyt ạ̹ny lwḥdy wạlṣdyq ḥty̱ msẖ jnby

[V8]
 tyjy bḥb wtsnd ḍʿfy .. whạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk .. hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk

[V9]
 ạ̉nạ bạṭlb mnk tmlạny brwḥk ạgẖmr kl kyạny

[V10]
 tyjy wtmlạ qlby ạ̉gẖạny .. whạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk .. hạfḍl ạ̉ḥbk</lyrics>
<author>ʿlạʾ rạḍy, jwrj fwzy</author>
